trans-unit.source: Contains the settings for the supported versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Contiene le impostazioni per le versioni supportate del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: There are currently two versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol supported by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
trans-unit.target: Attualmente sono disponibili due versioni del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging supportate da [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 e WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.

trans-unit.source: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 viene restituito dalla proprietà <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A>, mentre WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 viene restituito dalla proprietà <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the default version of WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce la versione predefinita del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the default version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Istanza derivata da <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> che rappresenta la versione predefinita del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: Gets version 1.1 of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene la versione 1.1 del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 version.
trans-unit.target: Istanza derivata da <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> che rappresenta la versione WS-ReliableMessaging1.1.

trans-unit.source: Gets the February 2005 version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene la versione di febbraio 2005 del protocollo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 version.
trans-unit.target: Istanza derivata da <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> che rappresenta la versione WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
